    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exciting turn-based strategy and supernatural investigation game</strong> where you dive into the dark world of paranormal creatures. As part of the <strong>Monster Hunters</strong> organization, your mission is to identify, hunt, and capture creatures like <strong>ghosts, vampires, demons, doppelgängers,</strong> and <strong>animatronics</strong>, while uncovering the dark secrets hidden among humans.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monster investigation and hunting:</strong> Interrogate suspects and use advanced tools like the <strong>vampire mirror</strong> and <strong>EMF meter</strong> to reveal who is a monster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turn-based strategy:</strong> Every encounter challenges you to make tactical decisions, with dynamic combat where you'll use items like <strong>silver bullets</strong> and <strong>holy water</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple supernatural entities:</strong> Face over 7 different types of creatures, each with their own weaknesses and special abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill development and inventory customization:</strong> Upgrade your hunting tools and abilities as you face increasingly powerful monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive narrative:</strong> Uncover the dark secrets monsters hide among humans as you solve the mysteries surrounding each case.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re passionate about supernatural horror and tactical games, <strong>&quot;That's My Monster: Neighbor Among Us&quot;</strong> offers a unique experience, filled with tension, strategic decisions, and a mysterious atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to face the supernatural and become the ultimate hunter?</strong> The hidden truth is waiting for you!</p>",
